Whoa...stupid mistake....Cloak and Dagger is the uploader not a tag....rofl.
Sorry for the mis-read.

Good torrent, worth reading (or listening to).  Only thing to know is author confuses introverts with the highly sensitive.  What she's really describing are characteristics of highly sensitive people, about 30% of whom, based on studies, are extraverts.  She was actually told this during her research, but being a lawyer by training, as well as a journalist, rather than research psychologist, she didn't grasp it.
